        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 6 at 3:21AM MDT until August 7 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...High temperatures of 100 to 106 degrees are expected.

* WHERE...Crowley, Otero, Bent, and Prowers.

* WHEN...From 11 AM to 8 PM MDT Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
